metadata.name: sentire
metadata.description:
Inspired by the books I've read and movies I've seen, this work is a representation that no matter how small you feel you might be, you can still be happy and make a good difference in the world.

Similar to fairy tales, a woman raises a little fairy to help them realise their life is more impactful than they think. 

You don't need great amounts of power as it's the small good deeds of kindness that keeps life beautiful.
